Valmet Automotive Logo
Valmet Automotive is a contract manufacturer and service provider for the automotive industry. The company offers services in automotive engineering, vehicle manufacturing, mobility solutions as well as in kinematic and convertible roof systems. Valmet Automotive’s focus areas are premium cars, convertibles, electric vehicles. The company has over 5,000 employees in Finland, Germany, Poland, and Spain. The headquarters are located in Uusikaupunki, Finland. The majority of the company is owned by Pontos Group and Finnish government-owned holding company Tesi.
